headline: Amphenol to Acquire CommScope’s Connectivity, Cable Solutions Unit for $10.5B
summary: Amphenol Corporation (NYSE:APH) is one of the best performing S&P 500 stocks to buy now. On August 4, Amphenol announced an all-cash deal to acquire CommScope Holding Company Inc.’s (NASDAQ:COMM) connectivity and cable solutions unit for $10.5 billion.
